OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,FDon Sheppard, Age 104, Royal Engineers
OL,8,FInterviewed 17 July 2023
OL,10,FDied 6 September 2024
OL,12,FLanding on Juno Beach on D-Day, Mr
OL,13,FSheppard was a Sapper in the Royal
OL,14,FEngineers who'd already served in
OL,15,FAfrica and Sicily.
OL,17,FAs a motorbike dispatch rider, he was
OL,18,Fpart of the 151 Brigade Highland
OL,19,FDivision supporting Canadian troops.
