OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,FAt that time some vessels were strafed
OL,7,Fby German fighters. On 6 June they
OL,8,Fmade the journey to the French coast.
OL,10,F"We had all the battleships firing
OL,11,Fover our heads and the Germans
OL,12,Freturning the fire," he said.
OL,14,F"We couldn't get right up to the beach
OL,15,Fand the first car off was a staff car
OL,16,Fwith an officer and a driver and it
OL,17,Fcompletely sank - the two of them got
OL,18,Fout.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
