OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Don
OL,4,CSheppard
OL,6,F"Young fellas didn't get off the boat
OL,7,Fand they were dead. The first thing
OL,8,Fyou learn when you go in the Army is
OL,9,Fhow to kill someone. Why? You didn't
OL,10,Fknow them.
OL,12,F"The Germans were just human beings
OL,13,Flike us. Over the years that's what I
OL,14,Fhave thought about."
